            <title>[PIG-1557] couple of issue mapping aliases to jobs</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-1557</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I have a simple script:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A = load &apos;/user/pig/tests/data/singlefile/studenttab10k&apos; as (name, age, gpa);&lt;br/&gt;
B = group A by name;&lt;br/&gt;
C = foreach B generate group, COUNT(A);&lt;br/&gt;
D = order C by $1;&lt;br/&gt;
E = limit D 10;&lt;br/&gt;
dump E;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I noticed a couple of issues with alias to job mapping: neither load(A) nor limit(E) shows in the output&lt;/p&gt;</description>
